00047 /*
00048    The application must update next_in and avail_in when avail_in has
00049    dropped to zero. It must update next_out and avail_out when avail_out
00050    has dropped to zero. The application must initialize zalloc, zfree and
00051    opaque before calling the init function. All other fields are set by the
00052    compression library and must not be updated by the application.
00053 
00054    The fields total_in and total_out can be used for statistics or
00055    progress reports. After compression, total_in holds the total size of
00056    the uncompressed data and may be saved for use in the decompressor
00057    (particularly if the decompressor wants to decompress everything in
00058    a single step).
00059 */
